sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>(Envoy)
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>4180/TCP HTTP
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider /<br/>OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Application
    participant Redis as Redis (optional)<br/>6379/TCP

    Note over AuthProxy,RBACProxy: PROXY_MODE selects which binary runs

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 1: Browser-Based OIDC Authentication (auth mode)
        Browser->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/start<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        AuthProxy->>OIDC: Redirect to authorization endpoint<br/>HTTPS/443, OAuth2 client ID + PKCE
        Browser->>OIDC: Login with credentials<br/>HTTPS/443
        OIDC->>AuthProxy: Redirect to /oauth2/callback<br/>Authorization code + state
        AuthProxy->>OIDC: POST token endpoint<br/>HTTPS/443, Client credentials + code + PKCE verifier
        OIDC-->>AuthProxy: Access token + ID token + refresh token
        AuthProxy->>Redis: Store session (if Redis backend)<br/>TCP/6379
        Redis-->>AuthProxy: OK
        AuthProxy-->>Browser: Set session cookie + redirect
        Browser->>AuthProxy: Request with session cookie
        AuthProxy->>Upstream: Proxied request<br/>X-Forwarded-User, X-Forwarded-Email headers
        Upstream-->>AuthProxy: Response
        AuthProxy-->>Browser: Proxied response
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Gateway,Upstream: Flow 2: K8s SA Token Validation (rbac mode)
        Gateway->>RBACProxy: Request with Bearer SA token<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS 1.2+
        RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: TokenReview (authn)<br/>HTTPS/443, In-cluster SA token
        K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: TokenReview response<br/>(user info, audiences)
        RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview (authz)<br/>HTTPS/443, In-cluster SA token
        K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: SubjectAccessReview response<br/>(allowed: true/false)
        alt Authorized
            RBACProxy->>Upstream: Proxied request<br/>x-remote-user, x-remote-groups headers
            Upstream-->>RBACProxy: Response
            RBACProxy-->>Gateway: Proxied response
        else Denied
            RBACProxy-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Browser,OIDC: Flow 3: OpenShift OAuth Logout (auth mode)
        Browser->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/sign_out<br/>Session cookie
        AuthProxy->>K8sAPI: DELETE OAuthAccessToken<br/>HTTPS/443, In-cluster SA token
        K8sAPI-->>AuthProxy: Token deleted
        AuthProxy->>OIDC: RP-initiated logout (optional)<br/>HTTPS/443, ID token hint
        OIDC-->>AuthProxy: Logout confirmed
        AuthProxy-->>Browser: Clear session cookie + redirect
    end

    rect rgb(245, 245, 255)
        Note over Gateway,AuthProxy: Flow 4: Envoy ext_authz Check (auth mode)
        Gateway->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/auth<br/>HTTP/4180 (pod-local)
        alt Authenticated
            AuthProxy-->>Gateway: 202 Accepted<br/>X-Auth-Request-User headers
        else Not Authenticated
            AuthProxy-->>Gateway: 401 Unauthorized
        end
    end
